{"tid":430681,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我留意左好耐，連登真係好多痴線佬","createTime":"2017-10-10T04:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T02:57:29.000Z","uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8f93250650bd52c5f85452ad5d465f977fc90d","tid":430681,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T04:29:04.000Z","msg":"1. 奶波魔<br />\n<br />\n真人應該好撚窮日日起籠屋入面出post。"},{"pid":"9c4a8df6b8fdb091e7ebc9d446e103bbf75de153","tid":430681,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"2. 老納<br />\n<br />\n自以為幽默既傻撚。"},{"pid":"9e6dca37d62433bb12fc705b299afb14f7ae53bd","tid":430681,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"3. 老貓再世<br />\n<br />\n失業IT廢中。"},{"pid":"78953bc7c98a0b678f6b243080fb440fcbc34761","tid":430681,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f09894054f0772f59b250edab745d1175976419","tid":430681,"uid":20448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"4 肥絲大隻<br />\n正宗垃圾廢物過街老鼠"},{"pid":"f773eeafa22c82a6f2224d4cab82b843c02a057a","tid":430681,"uid":43189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:05:14.000Z","msg":"無人識你咁撚慘呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫下你手<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>樓主 <strong>我唔係屈機男 #40470</strong> 簡介:<br />\n<br />\n於高登經常扮有錢佬教化眾高登仔做人道理, 被會員 米已成炊 質疑其有錢背景, 及後屈機男發明捐錢比賽及第一次敗走退出高登 (但事後依然有鬼鼠上高登)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114008_cf5793938b321b67b3b667655b375703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114008_cf5793938b321b67b3b667655b375703.jpg&h=ae37653c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114421_6bd8407bf6d5ceee8602e3fad4c3511f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114421_6bd8407bf6d5ceee8602e3fad4c3511f.jpg&h=7048e721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/113834_85b6f89b41cae26786ac72365fff771b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F113834_85b6f89b41cae26786ac72365fff771b.jpg&h=0192c6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/113811_db3a17f7bcac837ecc1fe2bc630a5473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F113811_db3a17f7bcac837ecc1fe2bc630a5473.jpg&h=ac60eca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屈機男 敗走後在連登重新插旗, 廣納信徒, 繼續以有錢佬姿態教化蒼生...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114136_20d860a4ad7eeb3a978fe80fdf4162f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114136_20d860a4ad7eeb3a978fe80fdf4162f7.jpg&h=b2af6d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會員 米已成炊 狙擊趕至, <strong>我唔係屈機男</strong> 發起第2次鬥捐錢活動, 並再次以<strong>敗者永久退出連登</strong>為賭注<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/216195/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/216195/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114554_d63c6683aa8e5ec7011afc9beb8e082e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114554_d63c6683aa8e5ec7011afc9beb8e082e.jpg&h=56996aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次結果更加柒, 自己開盤自己潛水, 會員 米已成炊 不戰而勝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/217870/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/217870/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114851_dd793b0a7bdc7b6717320a1b5602eb1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114851_dd793b0a7bdc7b6717320a1b5602eb1a.jpg&h=0c512bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日走數狗 <strong>我唔係屈機男 #40470</strong> 言而無信又再一次上水...</blockquote>"},{"pid":"be97e785ec181fd7e8cc111066be22433467ab31","tid":430681,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人識你咁撚慘呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫下你手<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>樓主 <strong>我唔係屈機男 #40470</strong> 簡介:<br />\n<br />\n於高登經常扮有錢佬教化眾高登仔做人道理, 被會員 米已成炊 質疑其有錢背景, 及後屈機男發明捐錢比賽及第一次敗走退出高登 (但事後依然有鬼鼠上高登)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114008_cf5793938b321b67b3b667655b375703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114008_cf5793938b321b67b3b667655b375703.jpg&h=ae37653c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114421_6bd8407bf6d5ceee8602e3fad4c3511f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114421_6bd8407bf6d5ceee8602e3fad4c3511f.jpg&h=7048e721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/113834_85b6f89b41cae26786ac72365fff771b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F113834_85b6f89b41cae26786ac72365fff771b.jpg&h=0192c6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/113811_db3a17f7bcac837ecc1fe2bc630a5473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F113811_db3a17f7bcac837ecc1fe2bc630a5473.jpg&h=ac60eca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屈機男 敗走後在連登重新插旗, 廣納信徒, 繼續以有錢佬姿態教化蒼生...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114136_20d860a4ad7